registry.title: IANAolsrv2LinkMetricType-MIB
registry.description: This MIB module defines the IANAolsrv2LinkMetricType Textual Convention, and thus the enumerated values of the olsrv2LinkMetricType object defined in the OLSRv2-MIB.
